snippet.title: Dragonstomper for the Atari 2600
snippet.description:
Not only really fun, but also innovative!

Yes, because of THIS game, you have games like the DragonQuest\DragonWarrior and Final Fantasy series, and other JRPGS!

And usually I don't say anything about the cover arts of a game, but this one is amazing. Yes, there is only one being, but less is sometimes more. ;)

Also, I wanted to show you the "Maniac", but sadly, I died before I could. :/
